Select what part you want to Modify, and change things on the Model.  When you find the part you want, you may Apply it to yourself.  You may also back out and apply multiple parts at once.
   Mod builders should add custom restrictions and notes here.

1: Take Off Your Clothes!  if you leave clothes on, some changes will not apply to you.  quit the conversation, strip, and try again.  it still may not work until someone else speaks to the model.

2: Bones & RDD Wings:  these might not apply from you to the model.  adjust manually.  there may also be restrictions in place to prevent you from gaining or losing bones/rdd wings.  ask the module admins.

3: Monk Eyes: your eyes will not apply to the model; apply manually.  you cannot REMOVE monk eyes, no matter what you do.
